node.title: Police locate body believed to be missing KaitƒÅia man
node.content: ["Police have located a body in Kait\u0101ia on Friday they believe is missing man Loren Charles Ross-Taylor.", "Formal identification is still ongoing, but the body was found seven kilometres away in Kait\u0101ia, which the police believe is Ross-Taylor.", "The 32-year-old was last seen on December 8 near Awanui Bridge.", "Police's thoughts are with his family and friends, and the matter will be referred to the coroner."]
